## Main
Let x: Int where x > 0 be 5.
Assert that x is equal to 5.
Trust that x is greater than 0 because "set to 5 above".
Check that x is at least 1.
If x is between 1 and 10:
    Show "small".
If x is even or x is divisible by 3:
    Show "structured".
